Blocks.Text: GERALD E. SMITH, RECORDER OF DEEDS
NOTE: I, the undersigned Recorder of Deeds, do hereby certify that the information shown on this Certification
Sheet as to the TYPE OF INSTRUMENT, the NAMES of the GRANTOR and GRANTEE as well as the
DESCRIPTION of the REAL PROPERTY affected is furnished merely as a convenience only, and in the case
of any discrepancy of such information between this Certification Sheet and the attached Document, the
ATTACHED DOCUMENT governs. Only the DOCUMENT NUMBER, the DATE and TIME of filing for
record of the recorded Document is taken from this CERTIFICATION SHEET.
I, the undersigned Recorder of Deeds for said County and State, do hereby certify that the following and annexed
instrument of writing, which consists of 3 pages, (this page inclusive), was filed for record in my office on
the 31 day of March 2022 at 10:01 am and is truly recorded as the document number printed above.
In witness whereof I have hereunto set my hand and official seal the day, month and year aforesaid.
THE OF SEAL ************************* OF ********* FOR COUNTY LOUIS
Recording Requested By: RICHMOND MONROE GROUP, INC.
When Recorded Return To: JESSICA BROWN, RICHMOND MONROE GROUP, INC., P.O. BOX 458,
CORPORATE ASSIGNMENT OF DEED OF TRUST
Grantor(s): SRP 2013-1, LLC, at 601 BRICKELL KEY DR., STE 700, MIAMI, FL, 33131
Grantee(s): ATC2021 TRUST, at C/O RICHLAND & FALKOWSKI, PLLC, 5 FAIRLAWN DRIVE, STE 204,
For value received, the Grantor does hereby grant, sell, assign, transfer and convey, unto the above-named
Grantee all interest under that certain Deed of Trust Dated: 5/31/2001, in the amount of $49,930.37, executed by
LADONNA DIXON A SINGLE WOMAN to CENTEX HOME EQUITY CORPORATION and Recorded: 7/3/2001,
Instrument #: 446, Book: 13139, Page: 1938 in ST LOUIS County, State of Missouri.
SITUATED IN ST. LOUIS COUNTY, MISSOURI, TO-WIT:
LOT 15 IN BLOCK 53 OF CASTLE POINT UNIT NUMBER 3 A SUBDIVISION IN ST. LOUIS COUNTY, MISSOURI,
ACCORDING TO THE PLAT THEREOF RECORDED IN PLAT BOOK 29 PAGE 11 OF THE ST. LOUIS COUNTY
TO HAVE AND TO HOLD, the same unto Grantee, its successors and assigns, forever, subject only to the terms and
conditions of the above-described Deed of Trust.
On March 28, 2022, before me, Jessica Brown, a Notary Public in and for STONE in the State of MISSOURI,
personally appeared KALEENA OGO, ASSISTANT VICE PRESIDENT, SRP 2013-1, LLC, personally known to me
(or proved to me on the basis of satisfactory evidence) to be the person(s) whose name(s) is/are subscribed to the
within instrument and acknowledged to me by means of X physical presence or
he/she/they executed the same in his/her/their authorized capacity, and that by his/her/their signature on the
instrument the person, or the entity upon behalf of which the person acted, executed the instrument.
WITNESS JassiBon my hand and official seal,
